The instructions provided walk you through the process, step by step. Start with the type of item you gave up as requested in Part I, Line 1. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a1/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a1/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Proceed to Line 2 in answering the remainder of the questions beginning with the article you received in return. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4e/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet2.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4e/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet2.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Lines 3 through 6 explain the history of the exchange. Fill out each one with the appropriate date-related information. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/2b/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet3.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/2b/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet3.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The next few questions are in Part II and pertain to any related party who might have been involved in the transaction. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e7/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet4.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e7/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet4.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Part III considers the actual financial value of the transaction. Lines 12 through 14 need only be completed if your transaction was not actually a "like-kind" exchange. Otherwise, go to Line 15. You most likely will not have any taxes to pay and provide this information for knowledge purposes. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/68/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet5.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet5.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/68/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet5.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Part IV deals with any possible "conflict of interest" issues you may incur. It will only pertain to instances where a higher replacement value takes place after noting the original item's value. This is particularly important for people in any job of power (government or otherwise) to consider. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet6.jpg/v4-459px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet6.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e3/Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet6.jpg/v4-759px-Fill-Out-Form-8824-Step-2Bullet6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
